data.description: Embrace the tranquility of this serene property, ideally situated between DFW & Waco. This cozy brick home features 3 bedrooms & 2 tastefully updated bathrooms, complemented by fresh interior & exterior paint. Inside, the open kitchen & living room with a wood-burning fireplace creates a soothing atmosphere. Step outside to a private oasis, complete with a spacious covered patio & hot tub. The property also offers a generous 900 sq-ft shop with a carport, kitchen, half bath, & private room, all spray foam insulated. A large garage door with an automatic opener provides convenient access. Covered RV concrete pad with a 50 AMP hookup. Ample storage space is provided by two substantial sheds & a versatile finished shed. The property is enclosed by new 6-barbed wire fencing, with cross pole fencing on the inside. Peaceful 2-stall horse barn up front, while a serene pond graces the back of the property. Don't miss the chance to experience a life of tranquility, convenience, & comfort.
